16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/68166325853d7212269252e4226fe818.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" media="(max-width: 1023px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/68166325853d7212269252e4226fe818.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/51e77fefab4f94dda92bd263f62e59ff.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" type="image/webp"/><img alt="数字人" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/51e77fefab4f94dda92bd263f62e59ff.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image"/></picture><div class="QYruxS"><div class="uQ8AfH"><span>数字人</span></div><p>提供海量数字人形象和声音，支持定制数字人形象</p></div></div></li><li class="J0Qcn6"><div class="PS_8oF"><picture class="DmHw0a"><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/a7bdf25b4341de254061023d37a5774d.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" media="(max-width: 1023px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/a7bdf25b4341de254061023d37a5774d.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/d1d71884f1c8c86ce0140a5f9154d3c6.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" type="image/webp"/><img alt="文本朗读" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/d1d71884f1c8c86ce0140a5f9154d3c6.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image"/></picture><div class="QYruxS"><div class="uQ8AfH"><span>文本朗读</span></div><p>支持选择热门音色或者音色克隆对文本进行朗读</p></div></div></li><li class="J0Qcn6"><div class="PS_8oF"><picture class="DmHw0a"><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/5a415903025c50e9faeadaba5cc940f1.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" media="(max-width: 1023px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/5a415903025c50e9faeadaba5cc940f1.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><source srcSet="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/d22e4ec35d7b470f9bdafc2809d67261.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" type="image/webp"/><img alt="smart-search-material" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="//p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/d22e4ec35d7b470f9bdafc2809d67261.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image"/></picture><div class="QYruxS"><div class="uQ8AfH"><span>智能搜索素材</span></div><p>精准识别并快速定位素材</p></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class="mtTimA"><h2 class="l3GrCe">专业剪辑 轻松剪出大片</h2><div class="Mr7L_R"><div class="ulamOK"><ul class="TpZY9e"><li class="TUyIxj Sx_NrL"><span>蒙版</span><p class="q5U5ky">支持添加线性、圆形、文字、钢笔等多种形式，轻松实现创意转场、惊喜抠像、局部特效。</p></li><li class="TUyIxj"><span>关键帧</span><p class="q5U5ky">只需设置起点和终点，即可自动生成流畅过渡。无论是移动、缩放还是淡入淡出，关键帧让视频创作更自由、更专业！</p></li><li class="TUyIxj"><span>调色</span><p class="q5U5ky">支持色轮、HSL、色相饱和度曲线、浮点调色、RGB曲线，轻松实现各种色彩效果。</p></li><li class="TUyIxj"><span>多机位</span><p class="q5U5ky">通过自动、声音方式精准对齐，可在4机位或9机位模式下，轻松实现多角度流畅切换。</p></li><li class="TUyIxj"><span>多时间线</span><p class="q5U5ky">在一个草稿里创建多条时间线，新增上限可达50条，便于分区剪辑。</p></li><li class="TUyIxj"><span>音频剪辑</span><p class="q5U5ky">支持升降调、声音分离、立体声平衡、音频创作布局等能力，让你的创作声临其境，玩转声音创意。</p></li></ul></div><div class="ruja0k"><picture class="DmHw0a Er4NiA"><source srcSet="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/103ba53a1feb6150655a8928356f448e.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" type="image/webp"/><img alt="mask" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/103ba53a1feb6150655a8928356f448e.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image"/></picture><p class="rZbm5W">支持添加线性、圆形、文字、钢笔等多种形式，轻松实现创意转场、惊喜抠像、局部特效。</p></div></div></section><section class="TOc4FZ"><h2 class="qfXlPz">全能易用 服务各类创作场景</h2><div class="kjAZx5"><ul class="_gL7en"><li class="YdHlBq"><picture class="DmHw0a"><img alt="media-broadcast" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/f285baff7d46fac5d520ec7549ad57f2.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.awebp"/></picture><div class="RRU56U"><span class="L5ruTx">自媒体口播</span><p class="Ez7HgK">美颜美体、智能剪口播、人声美化、智能抠像</p></div></li><li class="YdHlBq"><picture class="DmHw0a"><source srcSet="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/ddbc21d6794a268d5f8620d519dec6eb.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" type="image/webp"/><img alt="video-editing" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/ddbc21d6794a268d5f8620d519dec6eb.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image"/></picture><div class="RRU56U"><span class="L5ruTx">影视综二创</span><p class="Ez7HgK">智能镜头分割、人声分离、文本朗读、AI音乐</p></div></li><li class="YdHlBq"><picture class="DmHw0a"><source srcSet="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/826aea1ba876d27a333821349a85a700.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" type="image/webp"/><img alt="marketing-promotion" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/826aea1ba876d27a333821349a85a700.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image"/></picture><div class="RRU56U"><span class="L5ruTx">政企宣传</span><p class="Ez7HgK">音色克隆、AI音乐、数字人、模板</p></div></li><li class="YdHlBq"><picture class="DmHw0a"><source srcSet="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/dfaf8bcf5ba9c130eec0171b964034d7.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.webp" type="image/webp"/><img alt="government-enterprise-promotion" loading="lazy" crossorigin="anonymous" fetchpriority="low" src="https://p16-seeyou-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-2zwwjm3azk-sg/dfaf8bcf5ba9c130eec0171b964034d7.png~tplv-2zwwjm3azk-image.image"/></picture><div class="RRU56U"><span class="L5ruTx">营销推广</span><p class="Ez7HgK">数字人、智能包装、营销成片、智能文案</p></div></li><li cla